{"tid":323102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［反駁外媒］哥哥讚社會主義優越：感謝黨和政府安排","createTime":"2017-07-15T10:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T11:48:22.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd215df579bb9aebbf30afc0b50f106201760ff0","tid":323102,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波家屬今天下午在瀋陽官方安排下，進行記者會，但只有劉曉波68歲哥哥劉曉光現身。<br />\n劉曉波的哥哥首先感謝中國政府，他說感謝黨和政府完成了家屬心願，把曉波善後處理的細緻周到，「完美，出乎意料」，他續稱「在救治劉曉波全過程中，體現了社會主義優越性，整合了中國乃至世界的肝癌專家，只有在中國能夠體現，實現了舉國體制的優越性。」<br />\n<br />\n他不斷重申，要感謝黨和政府，過程體現政府對家屬的人文關懷。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波家屬今天下午在瀋陽官方安排下，進行記者會，但只有劉曉波68歲哥哥劉曉光現身。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170715/1161821/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170715%2F1161821%2F&d=6PeF4ryuzgCoBqxV8cERmEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5227556a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170715/1161821/</a><br />\nI<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/15/185610_1ab350e0ef43507b66ce3cd34e03e073.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F15%2F185610_1ab350e0ef43507b66ce3cd34e03e073.jpg&h=d4b21b13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16f1630d2dd07f5d520ef5d54a7361b816614965","tid":323102,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:04:14.000Z","msg":"逼人讀d咁骨痺既文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b97c827464332d171d0823baa0d668129aef320","tid":323102,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>逼人讀d咁骨痺既文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n這就是中國. Jpg"},{"pid":"cd946cb98a817a69b887582901bba52daf45829c","tid":323102,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply